---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "Retail Store Valuation Calculator 2025 | Value Your Retail Business";
const description = "Calculate your retail store worth with industry multiples and SDE analysis. Free retail business valuation calculator with instant estimates and professional $39 reports.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
    <div class="article-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1>🏪 Retail Store Valuation Calculator 2025</h1>
        <p>Value Your Retail Business with Industry Multiples and SDE Analysis</p>
    </div>

    <div class="calculator-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h3>Calculate Your Retail Store Value Instantly</h3>
        <p>Get an accurate estimate of your retail business worth using our SDE-based methodology</p>
        <a href="https://thevaluationgenie.com/" class="cta-button" target="_blank">🚀 Calculate My Retail Store Value</a>
        <p><small>Free estimate • Professional $39 report available • Used by 10,000+ retail owners</small></p>
    </div>

    <article>
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>📊 Introduction to Retail Store Valuation in 2025</h2>
            <p>Retail store valuation has become more critical than ever in 2025, as the industry continues to evolve with changing consumer behaviors, e-commerce integration, and post-pandemic market dynamics. Whether you're planning to sell your retail business, seeking investment, or simply want to understand your store's worth, accurate valuation is essential for making informed decisions.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="sde-methodology">
            <h2>📈 SDE Methodology for Retail Stores</h2>
            <p>Seller's Discretionary Earnings (SDE) is the most accurate valuation method for small to medium-sized retail stores. SDE represents the true financial benefit to the owner-operator, making it ideal for businesses where the owner is actively involved.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="faq">
            <h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
                <h4>What is the average retail store valuation in 2025?</h4>
                <p>Retail store valuations typically range from $100K to $5M+, with most businesses valued between $200K and $1.5M. The exact value depends on retail category, location, financial performance, and market conditions. Convenience stores average 2.8x SDE, while specialty retailers can reach 4.0x+ SDE multiples.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</MainLayout>
